#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/bsdinstall/_index.adoc:120
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Disk partitions containing different operating systems make it possible "
#| "to install multiple operating systems on one computer.  An alternative is "
#| "to use crossref:virtualization[virtualization,virtualization] which "
